    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HAELE 3D - Portrait Studio Pro 是一款面向初学者到高级艺术家的 3D 面部解剖绘画参考工具。它提供丰富的可编辑角色、表情、灯光设置和环境，是学习绘制人脸和头部的宝贵资源。无论你的风格是写实、风格化、卡通、动漫或介于两者之间，这款易用的应用都能补充教程，帮助你从草图到完成练习肖像绘画或雕刻技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/a87ae24a618d924b0116fa4072a0e423.poster.avif?t=1771427939\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/a87ae24a618d924b0116fa4072a0e423.webm?t=1771427939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/a87ae24a618d924b0116fa4072a0e423.mp4?t=1771427939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/8ca06ce4e2a8f55931382f3581fc0f57.poster.avif?t=1771427939\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/8ca06ce4e2a8f55931382f3581fc0f57.webm?t=1771427939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/8ca06ce4e2a8f55931382f3581fc0f57.mp4?t=1771427939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/f5a30d1aad64c3ea6d6c42be2a83fd6f.poster.avif?t=1771427939\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/f5a30d1aad64c3ea6d6c42be2a83fd6f.webm?t=1771427939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056390/extras/f5a30d1aad64c3ea6d6c42be2a83fd6f.mp4?t=1771427939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相比 HAELE 3D - Portrait Studio Lite，本版本提供更多角色、预设、发型与胡须、表情和环境选项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>功能：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速访问可编辑的预设配置，简化工作流程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多种角色中选择，练习绘制不同面孔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用丰富的表情库，快速获取灵感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不同的面部特征、比例、肤色和材质自定义角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美容变化：更改发型、胡须、嘴唇上胡须和眉毛样式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过可调灯光控制氛围：3 个聚光灯（颜色、强度、位置），环境光（HDRI 贴图、强度），地面光（颜色、强度）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择 HDRI 背景或纯色背景，可切换地面显示，并自定义地面颜色及反射率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精细调整相机角度、位置和视场以获得完美参考。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保存并加载场景。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 意大利语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 保加利亚语<strong>*</strong>, 捷克语<strong>*</strong>, 丹麦语<strong>*</strong>, 荷兰语<strong>*</strong>, 芬兰语<strong>*</strong>, 希腊语<strong>*</strong>, 匈牙利语<strong>*</strong>, 印度尼西亚语<strong>*</strong>, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 韩语<strong>*</strong>, 挪威语<strong>*</strong>, 波兰语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙<strong>*</strong>, 罗马尼亚语<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong>, 瑞典语<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文<strong>*</strong>, 土耳其语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语<strong>*</strong>, 越南语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
